      "text": "quest Payload word 1 bit 0 is set to one) and the recipient accepts the requested parameters,  it",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        562.96,
        540.09,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0033",
      "text": "shall set the SBRP Request Accepted bit to zero (Accepted) and echo the requested Error Win-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        574.96,
        540.05,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0034",
      "text": "dow, Interval and Threshold parameters in words 2 and 3.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        586.96,
        377.93,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0035",
      "text": "When a request to set the reporting parameters is indicated (i.e., request Payload word 1 bit 0",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        610.96,
        539.91,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0036",
      "text": "is set to one) and the recipient does not accept the parameters as requested the recipient shall",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        622.96,
        540.01,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0037",
      "text": "set the SBRP Request Accepted bit to one and echo in words 2 and 3 those parameters that",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        634.96,
        539.93,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0038",
      "text": "are accepted. Values not accepted by the recipient shall be set to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        647.02,
        436.25,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0039",
      "text": "When a request to report the parameters is indicated (request Payload word 1 bit 1 is set to",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        671.02,
        539.91,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p125_s0040",
      "text": "one) the recipient shall set the SBRP Request Accepted bit to zero (Accepted) report the cur-",
